City of Eunice -- 5 Mills - Mayor & Bd. of Ald.
Race.SummaryText:
CITY OF EUNICE PROPOSITION

SUMMARY: 10 YEAR 5 MILLS PROPERTY TAX FOR PAYMENT OF SALARIES, BENEFITS AND RELATED EXPENSES FOR THE CITY'S POLICE DEPARTMENT AND FIRE DEPARTMENT.
Race.FullText: Shall the City of Eunice, State of Louisiana (the "City"), be authorized to levy a special tax of 5 mills on all the property subject to taxation in the City for a period of ten (10) years, beginning with the year 2004 and ending with the year 2013 for the purpose of payment of salaries, benefits and related expenses for the city's police department and fire department?
